{"word":"G5270 - ὑποκάτω - hypokátō - hoop-ok-at'-o - Under","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποκάτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypokátō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-ok-at'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Under</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"கீழே, கீழ் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"under, underneath"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G2736 - κάτω - kátō - kat'-o/2736\">G2736</a>; <i>down under</i>, that is, <i>beneath:</i> - under.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}